biz.sudden.designCoordination.teamFormation.bottomUp.noticeboardAlgorithm
Class State

java.lang.Object
  biz.sudden.designCoordination.teamFormation.bottomUp.noticeboardAlgorithm.State

public class State
extends java.lang.Object

A class to hold all the information within a single state Thus - it holds the states ID and the set of resources it contains. It also contains the set of resources free at the state in both the forwards and backwards chaining directions. (Forwards chaining is: A ; A -> B; A -> B -> C etc. Backwards is ... C ; B -> C etc).
